{"id": 2907, "genre": 1000, "title": "什么样的游戏会让你坚持玩到最后？", "description": "能够让你坚持到通关的游戏都得具备哪些基本素养？", "record_count": 13547, "comment_count": 59, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190419145537pzYBG7b5crN1wOSD.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-21T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5715, "title": "什么样的游戏会让你坚持玩到最后？", "content": "什么样的游戏会让你坚持玩到最后？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 340304, "content": "一个假期内能通关的，再多就放弃了", "image": "img/option/option/2019041914564539J8vLB4zZcRhTNb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 340305, "content": "难度适中，不过于简单，也不会卡在一关过不去", "image": "img/option/option/20190419145817sAk9g8YEHDhVUCRi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 340306, "content": "至少 rmb 玩家不会影响游戏公平", "image": "img/option/option/20190419150153LDuAzqS8c93fEiks.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 340307, "content": "能学到一些东西的，例如有史实、名胜古迹", "image": "img/option/option/20190419150258ncMrGRCfbyBVm6Z7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 340309, "content": "每一关都不同，剧情有持续新意", "image": "img/option/option/20190419150423OGgi9qbDVdtuxW4Q.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 340310, "content": "能和朋友一起的，没人陪基本上都玩不到最后", "image": "img/option/option/20190419150505sZ0Py1ORMIhXGU8B.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 340311, "content": "有多重剧情走向", "image": "img/option/option/20190419150814PXfNlO6tDSMW9VRq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 340312, "content": "没坚持玩到最后过，没结局的小游戏才是我的归属", "image": "img/option/option/20190421233311mhRnu1vBaJGM2PwH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}